Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,no thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's a misinterpretation
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.98,0:09:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,there's more to the story
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,about what it symbolizes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,see
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,because now you're forcing the patient
