Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.94,0:10:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't think it's a spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think spiritual responsibility is a much higher thing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to stand up for truth
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to stand up for truth
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to have the courage
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the conviction
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to stand up for truth
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,takes you right over 200
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,so I don't think he meant passivity
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,which calibrates about 180
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than standing up for truth
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,can we please have a photograph
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,of my husband
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah whatever
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry we have to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,see in nature passivity invites aggression
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.06,0:11:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,passivity invites aggression
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and it triggers the predator prey response
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,which is biologically deeply rooted
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the way to get your dog out of the cage is to get your dog out of the cage
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the way to get your dog out of the cage is to get your dog out of the cage is to get your dog out of the cage
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the way to get yourself attacked is to run from the attacker
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the way to get yourself attacked is to run from the attacker
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and now he can't resist the temptation
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the running rabbit pulls the wolf after him
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,even if the wolf had noticed him before
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.73,0:11:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,he notices him now
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,hi doc I didn't have a question
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to thank you for your teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.61,0:11:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the passivity is different than non-action
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,non-action
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,non-action is something else
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but non-action is also an internal discipline
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,now for non-action to occur you have to be selfless
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.06,0:12:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The karma of non-action. Selfless service is non-action. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, I'm wondering if the calibrated level that we reach in one life is the starting point for any future life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't asked that, because there are also the so-called inner planes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You might leave at one level, mature in some other plane, and re-enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never asked it, and if I ask, can I ask it from this audience, they'll probably get it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask about the inner planes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So it would be possible to go down as well as go up in those inner planes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. As far as I know, whatever your calibrated level is, when you leave, that's the dimension that you find yourself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's what you are, so you are only realizing your own reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.57,0:12:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to something different than that which you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:12:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can only breathe air, you won't find yourself underwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll find yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in an air-breathing dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This last is not knowable, and we often get the answer that it's not to mess with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. I brought you this gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It blessed me much. I hope it blesses you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.75,0:13:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I would love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants that sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Anywhere you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Right in this guy's new jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.91,0:13:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,October is the last time I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I do have one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.43,0:13:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Today you were explaining, as you have before, that the revelation of St. John was received in a visit to an astral dimension, and so-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:13:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,John.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, the book of Revelations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not called Saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. John, the author of the book of Revelation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.52,0:14:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.02,0:14:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that also true for when people see UFOs?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,UFOs or experience ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, there's the child's imagination, so it's hard to say what, in an individual instance, it may be coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it's astral projection, sometimes it's out of body, sometimes it's hysterical suggestions, sometimes it's hallucinations, and not too few of them were drinking malta when they saw them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also post-hypnotic suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.39,0:14:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In a deep trance, and I tell them that there's UFOs out there, and here's how you identify them, the next time you come to my office, you're going to tell me they saw UFOs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:15:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's mass suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When people start seeing them, everybody starts seeing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When nobody sees them, nobody sees them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Misinterpretation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, a naive child.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's not out of wickedness or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,People just, you know, are suggestible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.82,0:15:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a beautiful photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They have cameras that photograph nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get a picture with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.69,0:15:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They have cell phones that take pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's written in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They have cell phones that take pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, what next?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.59,0:16:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get my cell phone to go on or off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.57,0:16:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to figure out to get the on and off switch on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got all these little buttons on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave up right then and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, this was a perfect topic for me and also the question of the gentleman
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,before me because I'm a recovering ghost investigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Recovering ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And actually, your book, the one I've written all the notes in, I was very helpful
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and at work with the lower level astral entities.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And those, I can testify, those do exist and they can be very dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying they don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just saying a Geiger counter is not the right instrument to look for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.74,0:16:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Something occurred to me when you did the calibration with Susan earlier with the reincarnation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to lower forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When you first did that, of course, I can't remember exactly how you phrased it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but it occurred to me it might be possible that it came up with the yes answer because
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it may be possible for human spirits, if they get low enough, to incarnate into the lower
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,astral plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.74,0:17:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.74,0:17:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked it in the context of the Hindu belief that you would come back to this earth as
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,a lesser life form.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was contextualized it as the, as held by the Hindu traditional religion, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.74,0:17:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.74,0:17:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.74,0:17:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've been a rat, you come back as a rat, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Work your way up from ratness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you very much for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's been a great help in the work and the research I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I really appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very interesting research, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Duke University did a lot with paranormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.13,0:17:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a whole field of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Journal of Scientific Investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You read that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.89,0:18:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.81,0:18:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, thank you for all that you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.57,0:18:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been really blessed by your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.63,0:18:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're going to�
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're going to be in my mind for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think you're going to be in my mind for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're going to be in my mind for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to be able to do any thing in your life that I've ever liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.63,0:18:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.63,0:18:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In my mind is where I came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.63,0:18:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.63,0:18:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being so supportive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So, your book is actually on the internet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.63,0:18:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I did, the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I did read about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when I first read your book, I just instantly got a change in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Compassion came in and judgment fell apart for myself as well as others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it's as though I look up and I realize something's going to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but ego could not have told me, and the spirit just says,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,See? It's me. I'm working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.19,0:18:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Other times I have to really struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I got something that I hadn't even realized,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is I hold on to some adolescent kind of behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:19:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And I realize that that barrier seems to draw my own children's interaction
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,with me to be negative, and we kind of dance around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.09,0:19:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You become a fellow adolescent with your own adolescent?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that way, you know, and I didn't recognize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They pull up the adolescent in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.27,0:19:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rebellion or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Rebellion in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I can feel it coming up, and we just kind of do this dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And until today, I couldn't name it or understand it or see where the juice was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.49,0:19:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm wondering if it's in me, am I drawing it to me to get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you assume about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, do you tell them they're being rebellious when they're being rebellious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.14,0:19:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's like political arguments.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And we get in these silly arguments, and I think I need to be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.84,0:19:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought they thought they needed to be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:20:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm thinking I do, and then they get it from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You can present an alternate viewpoint and don't claim it as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha often did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He says, I have heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I have heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And then he presents an alternate way of looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.06,0:20:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't mean you should accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't mean it's my reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's presenting an alternate view.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have to agree with it right then and there either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's part of just my letting go of the juice of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The payoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.99,0:20:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I let go of the payoff of it all by just saying there's an alternative point of view and letting it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people would say, and then you'd give the other way, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think education helps so many things because, you know, we had a chance to be debaters, debating teams, debate club.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:20:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And you didn't know what your position was going to be until you pulled it out of a hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:20:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you began to see that, you know, you can corral argumentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And then that makes you more sophisticated and you don't identify with the view, then you see that alternate views is a sophisticated level of intellectual, you know, so you want a term to be more, more advanced intellectually then, see, and philosophic, encourage the reading of philosophy instead of a narrow spectrum, right and wrong, good and bad, you can't really say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.59,0:21:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just getting right around, good and bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, if you see the philosophic position behind your argument, then you can start addressing it from the impersonal level of philosophic theory, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.67,0:21:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I do with relativism.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.09,0:21:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.73,0:21:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I just look at the philosophic theory, put it together, and see if it proves out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.93,0:21:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, it collapses of its own weight because it's based upon nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.07,0:22:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't have to attack it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I just, you know, take, pull it out to its extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.71,0:22:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just reveal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.55,0:22:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if all, you know, if all positions are fallacious, then you're supporting relativism is obviously fallacious, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.57,0:22:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If all argumentation is stupid, then everything you're saying today is a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.09,0:22:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.18,0:22:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If there isn't a morality, then why get so moralistic about relativism?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.06,0:22:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in other words, the same as the skeptic, you know, the skeptic says, you can't believe anything the human mind says, except what he says, in which case it's the truth, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So the skeptic is not skeptic of all about his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.80,0:22:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not skeptic of all about skepticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.92,0:22:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's stupid and he's hung by his own petard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.60,0:22:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So I try to hang him up with his own petard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.26,0:22:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's no truth in argumentation, then you've just wasted ten minutes of my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Because your argumentation is stupid also, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.74,0:22:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.28,0:22:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a picture taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.24,0:23:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.82,0:23:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter says, don't argue with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.54,0:23:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.52,0:23:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the human mind is convinced that its view of the world is the real one, say.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.57,0:23:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And the skeptic thinks that, you know, skepticism is the way to truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.47,0:23:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The human mind is unable to arrive at truth, and skepticism itself is a total waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.68,0:23:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.09,0:23:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.17,0:23:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.85,0:23:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I just wanted to tell you that you've done it twice now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.91,0:23:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.27,0:23:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.52,0:23:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.08,0:23:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Was getting along just marvelous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.20,0:23:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuffling along, getting into this old age thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.36,0:24:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I had little old ladies opening the door for me, and I was loving this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.74,0:24:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you do, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.72,0:24:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.90,0:24:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was marvelous.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.10,0:24:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely marvelous.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.50,0:24:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I got your CD on old age.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.36,0:24:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And the whole thing went out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.34,0:24:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that bothers me, if I go back the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.96,0:24:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way I was, my wife is going to divorce me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.65,0:24:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, somewhere I have to give something up and move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.57,0:24:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The young man...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.26,0:24:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, because age is such a powerful program from beginning to end, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.10,0:24:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.70,0:24:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And we see it all through life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.74,0:24:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.87,0:24:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it isn't a thought form.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.51,0:24:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.01,0:24:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.55,0:24:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.83,0:24:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.11,0:25:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in life, you say, we're in middle age now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.61,0:25:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So, now we have this, and we have this, and by God, we do have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.15,0:25:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And maybe it's just natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.51,0:25:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it is natural, you know, a lot of these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.55,0:25:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.53,0:25:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.09,0:25:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.69,0:25:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And why avoid them?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.36,0:25:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.00,0:25:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.86,0:25:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get forgetful and rickety, so you get forgetful and rickety.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.72,0:25:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.26,0:25:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.66,0:25:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.70,0:25:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.72,0:25:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.74,0:25:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.78,0:25:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.80,0:25:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.90,0:25:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.06,0:25:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.12,0:25:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.18,0:25:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.22,0:25:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.26,0:25:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.28,0:25:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.70,0:25:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.20,0:25:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I resist, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.02,0:25:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.56,0:25:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.76,0:25:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.10,0:25:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.36,0:25:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.68,0:25:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.22,0:25:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.66,0:25:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm giving it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.78,0:25:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.64,0:25:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.52,0:25:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going back where I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.06,0:25:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.02,0:25:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.58,0:25:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one real question.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.56,0:25:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.06,0:25:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.34,0:25:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,For a friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.64,0:25:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.98,0:25:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.22,0:25:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.68,0:25:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been recently diagnosed, and he couldn't be here because this just happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.92,0:25:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.10,0:25:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.58,0:25:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He comes to your classes when he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.64,0:25:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.14,0:25:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.50,0:26:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been recently diagnosed with prostate cancer, very early stage with a high PSA.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.34,0:26:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.72,0:26:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.14,0:26:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's trying to address it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.34,0:26:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He has your CD.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.64,0:26:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.84,0:26:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's on health and these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.64,0:26:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's trying to address it with that and natural cures.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.46,0:26:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.72,0:26:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He came up with this as a product of a natural that helps the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.84,0:26:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.50,0:26:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And some friends of his have had positive results.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.64,0:26:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.14,0:26:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked if you would calibrate that on his behalf for him, if you can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.15,0:26:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.52,0:26:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an herbal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.52,0:26:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is a brand name, but I don't say what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.18,0:26:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.20,0:26:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.44,0:26:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such fine print, you have to use a magnifying glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.30,0:26:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your question is, is this beneficial to prostate problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.70,0:26:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,For him, specifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.12,0:26:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask a general.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.04,0:26:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.00,0:26:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.20,0:26:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.78,0:26:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.24,0:26:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.27,0:27:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.37,0:27:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is beneficial to prostate problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.63,0:27:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He says it's beneficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.15,0:27:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be beneficial to his prostate problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.07,0:27:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.39,0:27:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.95,0:27:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.23,0:27:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.87,0:27:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not talking about cures.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.11,0:27:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just beneficial, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.29,0:27:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Beneficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.75,0:27:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some other stuff they recommend for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.77,0:27:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I always forget the name of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.83,0:27:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a bottle of it at home, but I never get around to opening it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.01,0:27:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that's good for it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.65,0:27:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard another product called glutathione, you know, recommended to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.72,0:27:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there's nothing, nothing, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.52,0:27:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I believe everything is physical, mental, and spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.08,0:27:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.38,0:27:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So you cancel the thought form.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.96,0:27:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an infinite being.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.76,0:27:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not subject to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.90,0:27:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a belief system, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.54,0:27:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time, you take whatever you need, Flomax, so you can go to the bathroom where
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.80,0:27:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you couldn't before, and you pray about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.08,0:27:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do physical, mental, and spiritual on everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.66,0:27:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.16,0:27:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's physical, mental, and spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.48,0:27:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because you're doing the Course in Miracles doesn't mean you can't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.90,0:28:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to ask me for a headache, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.68,0:28:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's physical, mental, and spiritual, and I believe it should be approached on all
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.34,0:28:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,three simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.56,0:28:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In my practice back east and out here, I always put all of them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.72,0:28:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Physical, mental, spiritual, nutritional, acupuncture, whatever would help.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.28,0:28:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.80,0:28:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Vitamins, high-dose vitamins.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.46,0:28:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah, I appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.97,0:28:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.67,0:28:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I've had all those myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.49,0:28:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Acupuncture was a big help, but my back collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.86,0:28:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My vertebrae crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.86,0:28:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But it ain't one thing, it's another, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.31,0:28:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you both again for what you've been in our life and for everybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.73,0:28:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, you mentioned again today that the Buddha felt like he was beset by demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.73,0:28:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.13,0:28:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he ever say how he transcended it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.18,0:28:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He became fully enlightened in the end, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.22,0:29:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But as a book guy, you know, transcending levels, also I think a devotional non-duality,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.30,0:29:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I describe the levels from about 800 on.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.73,0:29:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,From about 800 on, you can be beset by all kinds of aches and pains and strange comings and goings and demons, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.77,0:29:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That which gains, that which has its total gain from falsehood, if you come from truth, you are its ultimate enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.11,0:29:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So you look like the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.31,0:29:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And it will attack you from every angle it can, look for every chink.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.37,0:29:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So these spiritual teachers who typically...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.13,0:29:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They're around in the 570s or so, tend to fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.69,0:29:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They become world famous and a lot of followers, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.81,0:29:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Next thing you read, they're into childhood seduction, sexual seduction, extortion of money, every kind of finagling.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.87,0:29:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the little demons look for where there's a chink in your armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.83,0:29:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They try a little flattery.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.55,0:29:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he liked that title, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.79,0:30:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl winked at him and said,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.71,0:30:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, I'd love to be with you, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.63,0:30:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And he says,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.59,0:30:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, everything is spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.55,0:30:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sex is spiritual, so let's do it for God.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.15,0:30:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.77,0:30:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You can rationalize anything, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.39,0:30:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's done by gurus.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.95,0:30:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's ladies who've been around and been to bed with a lot of gurus, and they've written books about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.25,0:30:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I've got books at home, the various gurus and the tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.32,0:30:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So the seduction of the innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.92,0:30:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel it's the fault of the spiritual teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.84,0:30:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did not know that it's his responsibility to warn students of where the weak sides are.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.92,0:30:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody thinks, well, I'm going to become spiritual and everything is going to be just beautiful and angels and flowers and perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.58,0:30:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're going to pull up that which is antithetical to purity.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.04,0:30:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to pull up its opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.39,0:30:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the attempts at seducing you and attacking you there with vanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.15,0:31:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So the spiritual ego is one of them, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.83,0:31:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.71,0:31:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.88,0:31:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And thinking that you're more than what you are, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.54,0:31:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the students see you that way doesn't mean that's what you are, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.77,0:31:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a beginner.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.63,0:31:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize that enlightenment in this realm is kindergarten when you're in the room for the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.21,0:31:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So anybody who calibrates at age 50 is moving fine in kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.76,0:31:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And I remind them, this is kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.46,0:31:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There are realms where it starts at a couple thousand, and you haven't even hit a thousand yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.86,0:31:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So to get humility back into this, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.56,0:31:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And to knock over the spiritual ego, each one of us, you know, even to a very high level, is only a servant of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.86,0:31:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And the archangels are so far beyond us, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.08,0:31:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So keeping those spiritual principles safeguards the student.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.88,0:31:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And just surrendering everything to God no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.90,0:32:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That which makes us living off falsehood certainly does not like integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.14,0:32:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't like truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.90,0:32:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Because its whole power base is based on falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.96,0:32:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So why should it like truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.25,0:32:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.34,0:32:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.70,0:32:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.70,0:32:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking for a chink.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.84,0:32:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did it get you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.84,0:32:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.84,0:32:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you might have touched this probably often.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.84,0:32:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was wondering if you could give some tips on surrendering to pay off.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.84,0:32:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And just one practice that I use is self-inquiry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.84,0:32:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I constantly contemplate, you know, my being and watch, just constantly watching the mind do its thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.84,0:32:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.34,0:32:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrendering to pay off.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.34,0:32:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wonder if you could give some tips on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.21,0:32:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The pay off of negativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.21,0:32:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.21,0:32:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,See.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.21,0:33:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, every negative feeling is held in place by a pay off.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.69,0:33:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So you look at what the pay off is.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.69,0:33:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to get rid of hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.78,0:33:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You just look at what is the pay off of the hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.98,0:33:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, don't ask yourself am I willing to give up hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.98,0:33:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask yourself am I willing to give up the pay off of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.98,0:33:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The feeling of rejection.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.10,0:33:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.10,0:33:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The glee of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.10,0:33:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.10,0:33:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So once you give up the pay off, then the thing tends to relinquish of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.23,0:33:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, then the next stack comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.78,0:33:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So you won't run out of suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.16,0:33:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off pride, then the anger comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.16,0:33:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the grief comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.16,0:33:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the remorse comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.16,0:33:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the self-hatred comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.58,0:33:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So each thing uncorks the stack.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.58,0:33:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And you work through the stack.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.58,0:33:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But the whole stack is held in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.58,0:33:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,By some projected value.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.58,0:33:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But the real value to the narcissistic core of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.58,0:33:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it feeds off it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.58,0:34:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.70,0:34:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the pay off of negativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.70,0:34:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,People would instantly give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.70,0:34:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So something must be keeping it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.47,0:34:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And you say what is keeping it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.60,0:34:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Can it be that I actually feel good to watch that SOB have a sword and put right through him?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.78,0:34:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.78,0:34:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He deserved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.94,0:34:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what you look for.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.38,0:34:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the secret pay off?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.38,0:34:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a secret narcissistic pay off.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.38,0:34:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Because people are ashamed of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.38,0:34:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So they don't want to admit that they're enjoying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.38,0:34:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They're enjoying all the grief and celebrity status of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.91,0:34:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And the attention they're getting.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.91,0:34:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.82,0:34:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You give it up, it tends to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.82,0:34:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.79,0:35:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.59,0:35:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My question actually was quite similar to the fellow just before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.59,0:35:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving up the juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.36,0:35:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,In one of your books, I believe it was I, you mentioned giving up the ego in one fell swoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.62,0:35:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of maybe looking at all the individual little things.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.62,0:35:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's the same as giving up the juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.62,0:35:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.62,0:35:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, giving up the juice is giving up specific negative feelings and viewpoints.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.62,0:35:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.46,0:35:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that similar to surrendering one's life to God in every moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.46,0:35:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.46,0:35:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,As we go along?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.46,0:35:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.46,0:35:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Because errors are going to come up, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.46,0:35:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But just to keep going and not...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.46,0:35:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Constantly surrendering to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.46,0:35:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you finally get...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.53,0:35:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I've ever written about it or talked about it in a group.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.53,0:35:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.53,0:35:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll come a time when I call it the final run.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.53,0:36:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, you're like desperate to read the truth and you're willing to drop everything in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.55,0:36:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk away from all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.55,0:36:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Titles, money, positions, houses, servants, everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.22,0:36:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're like, no, this is going to be the final run.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.42,0:36:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,On the final run, every second, you're releasing, surrendering, releasing, surrendering.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.45,0:36:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Every second.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.45,0:36:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And you do make very rapid progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.61,0:36:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You forget the body's even there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.93,0:36:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And I remember living all by myself doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.22,0:36:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was somebody in the mirror that scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.22,0:36:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked and there was somebody in the house, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.22,0:36:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.22,0:36:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Another time, I walked through a wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.22,0:36:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to walk through the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.22,0:36:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, in your etheric value, you walk through walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.22,0:36:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I walked through the wall and bang, my whole face got...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.22,0:36:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I bashed myself up against the solid wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.22,0:36:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.22,0:36:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You just transcended any identification with the physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.22,0:37:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You say it's Thursday and the last time you ate anything was Monday or Tuesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.22,0:37:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, and you're looking sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.22,0:37:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one apple and two Diet Pipsies and a piece of cheese and you haven't eaten this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.22,0:37:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.22,0:37:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you're on a drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.22,0:37:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And this drive will take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.22,0:37:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It will take you very far.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.22,0:37:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And once you get a drive like that, go with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.22,0:37:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Go with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.44,0:37:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Go with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.44,0:37:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.92,0:37:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The world will see you've gone mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.92,0:37:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.03,0:37:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gone mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.03,0:37:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Realize that you haven't gone mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.03,0:37:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't gone far enough yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.70,0:37:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Because in the world's view, you've gone mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.92,0:37:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.92,0:37:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.92,0:37:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm working with a guy that's in recovery right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.53,0:37:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm trying to help him, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.94,0:37:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's like into some of the things that you were showing on the slide today
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.30,0:37:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that, you know, aren't really that productive in spiritual progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.36,0:37:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes I feel like I want to tell him about it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.36,0:37:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I feel that that's like pride or some sort of positionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.42,0:38:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell him what you've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.42,0:38:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.42,0:38:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the Buddha said, I have heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.42,0:38:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I have heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.42,0:38:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can say, I have heard from, you know, a pretty advanced spiritual teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.42,0:38:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that this can have a very deleterious effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.42,0:38:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It is pleasant and exciting and fun as it can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.42,0:38:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I have heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.42,0:38:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's up to him, his karmic preparedness for listening to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.65,0:38:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, any?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.87,0:38:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.87,0:38:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.87,0:38:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,At a certain point, you'll do anything that you hear that is spiritually beneficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.90,0:38:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll drop anything that you think is spiritually negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.13,0:38:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And very often the news comes to you because you're innocent by somebody more advanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.13,0:38:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody more advanced, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.42,0:38:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I once had a person who could see auras tell me that such and such a teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.42,0:38:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,has no energy around the heart chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.42,0:38:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.42,0:38:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So that was information.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.42,0:38:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was ready to listen to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.42,0:38:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So I say, oh, what do you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.42,0:38:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.42,0:39:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can carry the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.42,0:39:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not up to you to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.42,0:39:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But to karmically responsible, I would like to know that I shared that information.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.42,0:39:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's his option now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.45,0:39:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So we carry the message and not the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.45,0:39:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.45,0:39:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We carry the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.45,0:39:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.45,0:39:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.45,0:39:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's our obligation as spiritually evolved to carry the message whenever we can at the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.45,0:39:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,level of the person's capacity and willingness to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.45,0:39:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.45,0:39:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.98,0:39:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.98,0:39:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.98,0:39:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.24,0:39:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about the duality of good and evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.35,0:39:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.14,0:39:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Back home, I have a friend that teaches a class.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.71,0:39:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And he teaches on the art of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.87,0:39:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's a very good teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.87,0:39:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's a very good teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.87,0:39:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And kind of puts it as a spiritual battle that we're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.19,0:40:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,During the war, the Calvary to 350, the ancient Chinese text, Liu Tzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.26,0:40:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I would assume he got some of the ideas from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.58,0:40:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's mainly centered around the ego that we're fighting or yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.83,0:40:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a class to alcoholics and addicts.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.83,0:40:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.83,0:40:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.83,0:40:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.83,0:40:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have a problem with the whole war because I think of the duality of good and evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.83,0:40:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I fighting a war?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.83,0:40:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on the good side of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.83,0:40:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to fight this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.83,0:40:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What war?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.83,0:40:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.83,0:40:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.83,0:40:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I'm trying to think of...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.83,0:40:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that there's spirits out there that are trying to attack you when you rise in
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.02,0:40:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.02,0:40:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.02,0:40:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't have to call it war.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.02,0:40:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the other side...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.70,0:40:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just being themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.70,0:40:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They ain't at war with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.70,0:40:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.70,0:40:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So there would be no necessary to look at it as a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.70,0:40:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.70,0:40:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.70,0:40:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't contextualize it as a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.70,0:40:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What would it be contextualized as?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.70,0:40:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.70,0:40:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The way nature responds at certain levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.62,0:41:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's natural to certain segments of the populace to rise up against that which does not agree
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.62,0:41:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.62,0:41:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.23,0:41:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego is always looking for agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.23,0:41:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So the ego, an enemy, is somebody that doesn't agree with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.67,0:41:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.67,0:41:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a matter of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.86,0:41:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,War is a projection of a contextualization.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.86,0:41:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You might say in nature you see the struggle for domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.08,0:41:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You see dominance all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.08,0:41:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Dominance.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.08,0:41:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Dominance.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.08,0:41:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the prevailing view should be dominant.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.62,0:41:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really an animal instinct, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.62,0:41:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, who cares if other people agree with yours, the way you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.55,0:41:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.55,0:41:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the defenselessness, I think of the course or just in defenselessness of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.93,0:41:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to engage in an active battle with your ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.93,0:41:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.93,0:41:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the wisdom of the Tao is Taoism, you know, as it's pronounced in English.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.93,0:42:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You bend with the reed, so let it go by with its viewpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.93,0:42:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to oppose communism.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.63,0:42:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I can just say, you know, if I calibrate it so much, I see its demonstration in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.63,0:42:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,stage, and to me it's not appealing to watch 100 million people starve to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.63,0:42:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Not appealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.92,0:42:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite his little red book.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.87,0:42:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to be his enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.13,0:42:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to conquer him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.13,0:42:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I certainly am not overwhelmed by his wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.42,0:42:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman Mao and his ilk.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.42,0:42:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So in recovery, in helping others, I mean, that's not fighting a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.48,0:42:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.48,0:42:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, because in recovery, you're sharing the truth without taking any position.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.48,0:42:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no opinion on outside matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.48,0:42:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.48,0:42:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But the disease of addiction sometimes seems as though it's an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.48,0:42:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.80,0:42:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a contextualization.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.80,0:42:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a spiritual opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.80,0:43:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Addiction is one of the fastest routes to conviction.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.28,0:43:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of the fastest routes to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.28,0:43:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's one of the fastest spiritual pathways.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.70,0:43:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, because addiction is such a narrow line, you can't turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.73,0:43:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only go straight ahead or die.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.73,0:43:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So either surrender or die.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.73,0:43:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes it easy, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.73,0:43:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.66,0:43:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care which way it is with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.66,0:43:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You go to meetings or die.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.91,0:43:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I care?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.91,0:43:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your convulsion is not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.74,0:43:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just trying to see over the duality of good and evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.42,0:43:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I understand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.42,0:43:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.42,0:43:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But instead of opposite, look at it as side by sides, you know, or positions on a thermometer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.34,0:43:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, this is right and this is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.34,0:43:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more like where is it in between, depending on the viewpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.41,0:43:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a subtle question.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.91,0:43:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a difficult one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.91,0:43:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.91,0:43:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem of good and evil, of course, has been around since Genesis, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.91,0:44:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.91,0:44:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The serpent and the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.58,0:44:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The serpent played on ease, childhood, naivete, innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.58,0:44:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, well, just move faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.58,0:44:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want now?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.58,0:44:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really have a question to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.58,0:44:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I just brought a gift, and I guess it's a two-fold gift because it was a thank you gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.58,0:44:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.58,0:44:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And just a happy birthday gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.58,0:44:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.65,0:44:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll sign this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.65,0:44:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's a couple of angels that I made, and they're made out of gold, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.65,0:44:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.65,0:44:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time we've been here physically.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.65,0:44:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But my husband has, I think, every one of your capes, and he's out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.65,0:44:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.65,0:44:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.65,0:44:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.65,0:44:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.65,0:44:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.97,0:44:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one question that I'd like to ask of Susan, because the kinesiology resonates with my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.97,0:45:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And so when I do it, and he doesn't necessarily get the answer that he wants, is it because that my resistance or if I'm not?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.97,0:45:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess with the way you do with your arm or whatever of how the resistance is, how do you know when there's a yes or a no?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.06,0:45:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't have a vested interest in the answer and still get a right answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.90,0:45:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.90,0:45:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be devoted to truth above gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.90,0:45:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,See, and one gain is being right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.06,0:45:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have to relinquish wanting to control the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.90,0:45:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll tell you, in return, you get a gift that is greater than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.90,0:45:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But you relinquished.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.90,0:45:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if you say, am I willing to relinquish control of this answer, you feel momentarily that you lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.67,0:45:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And then on the way to the bathroom, suddenly you got, man, I just saw the door that that opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.83,0:45:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're letting go positionality, and it's replaced by essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.83,0:46:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And out of essence, you see, oh, my God, good thing I didn't go that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.90,0:46:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.90,0:46:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And Ron Stock didn't do too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.90,0:46:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,After all.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.69,0:46:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess WorldCom wasn't the best investment, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.69,0:46:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.46,0:46:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.46,0:46:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to make it as concise as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.46,0:46:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A few years ago, I was walking down an avenue in Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.46,0:46:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And all of a sudden, every face, every person became lovable, even the sidewalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.52,0:46:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.52,0:46:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It lasted for a few moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.52,0:46:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But then an intense fear came over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.52,0:46:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.52,0:46:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, agonizing, that the I was disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.62,0:46:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, the questions that popped into my mind were, who would love my friends and family?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.62,0:46:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How would I function?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.62,0:46:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was like a nonverbal choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.62,0:47:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I could give up the I and stay there in this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.62,0:47:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.62,0:47:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a glimpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.62,0:47:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.62,0:47:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.62,0:47:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you weren't prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.62,0:47:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But now you know that it's going to recur, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.62,0:47:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So you got a premature glimpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.62,0:47:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So that you can adjust your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.65,0:47:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That when it becomes dominant, you won't, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.74,0:47:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I walked away from everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.74,0:47:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.74,0:47:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything this world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.74,0:47:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Money, title, wealth, state, home, titles.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.74,0:47:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.00,0:47:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I walked away.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.00,0:47:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.00,0:47:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was prepared to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.00,0:47:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I saw what was coming, and I thought, see, what's coming is so far beyond all that
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.86,0:47:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.86,0:47:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That it's easy to let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.86,0:47:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.86,0:47:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, well, it must have been difficult to let go of all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.86,0:47:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to what you saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.86,0:47:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.86,0:47:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can remember one time, 12 people being at dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.90,0:47:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.90,0:47:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, all of them turned into Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.90,0:47:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I like saw the Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.90,0:47:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the Christ in all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.90,0:48:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Literally saw the Christ shine forth in all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.09,0:48:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to adjust your life when that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.09,0:48:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.09,0:48:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have a glimpse, and that's more than love.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.09,0:48:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a glimpse, and that warns you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.09,0:48:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's what's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.09,0:48:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.09,0:48:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the reality, the essence of the divinity of all of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.09,0:48:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.09,0:48:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess, and just a follow-up to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.09,0:48:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,After you cross the final doorway, is there any individual aspect left?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.09,0:48:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That was like a secondary fear that came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.09,0:48:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I left the I, would there be anything, like an individual awareness?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.09,0:48:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Or would there be something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.09,0:48:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.09,0:48:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.09,0:48:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.09,0:48:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.09,0:48:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.09,0:48:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.09,0:48:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.09,0:48:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.09,0:48:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.09,0:48:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.09,0:48:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.09,0:48:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.09,0:48:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it really matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.87,0:48:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.21,0:48:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.57,0:48:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.55,0:48:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens is the dimension of existence changes, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.43,0:49:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The dimension changes, in which there's no longer a personal locus.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.57,0:49:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the truck is running itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.77,0:49:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.11,0:49:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,because the truck is built that way, but there's nobody at the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.72,0:49:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You witness the truck running down the highway the way it's supposed to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.93,0:49:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's no personal self.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.33,0:49:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is happening autonomously and spontaneous of its own,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.43,0:49:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,because what you're seeing is a potentiality eventuating into an actuality,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.33,0:49:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,such as you're coming up here was a potentiality, now it's an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.13,0:49:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no cause of it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.10,0:49:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.80,0:49:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But your energy and my energy pull each other together just like that at that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.10,0:49:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's doing it of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.14,0:49:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.49,0:49:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.72,0:49:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.43,0:49:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And the back of your bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.49,0:49:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.29,0:49:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. I have no question, I just have thank yous.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.49,0:49:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.98,0:49:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.88,0:50:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.38,0:50:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.00,0:50:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.90,0:50:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you didn't hear me. I said I have no questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.30,0:50:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you have no questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.60,0:50:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.50,0:50:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.20,0:50:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.00,0:50:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.30,0:50:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The question was, what will you say if I have no questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.50,0:50:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So I answered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.37,0:50:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.87,0:50:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.67,0:50:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain to me about angels and what they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.87,0:50:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not an expert on angels, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.67,0:50:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.76,0:50:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I just haven't had time to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.66,0:50:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.60,0:50:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I know something about archangels that they calibrate, you know, 50,000,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.51,0:50:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and the angelic memories I have, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.31,0:50:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.01,0:50:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.14,0:50:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And an experiential reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.39,0:50:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have a memory of greeting people as they came across in a state of shock,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.54,0:51:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,just hit by a bus, coming across through a different dimension,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.71,0:51:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and through the love that shone forth that eliminated their fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.42,0:51:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a memory of that, you know, an angelic kind of experience, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.10,0:51:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.60,0:51:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know angels have come to me in physical bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.60,0:51:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, they even calibrate whether I'm an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.60,0:51:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.80,0:51:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.40,0:51:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The most ridiculous impossibility, and then along would come just the person
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.76,0:51:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,who didn't even know you were there, hundreds of miles away,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.78,0:51:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and just happened to come up at a moment of crisis, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.06,0:51:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, well, that's accidental.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.56,0:51:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the chances would be one in a hundred million.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.36,0:51:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it happens over and over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.76,0:51:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you realize why people do the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.85,0:51:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They call it Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.45,0:52:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm predictable, unlikely, statistically impossible, but there it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.91,0:52:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.31,0:52:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend asked me to give this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.41,0:52:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So my question is, you talked about Muhammad when he was transcribing the Koran.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.21,0:52:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He was at 720 or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.61,0:52:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He was around 700, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.01,0:52:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you said he had temporal lobe epilepsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.01,0:52:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the probable explanation, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.61,0:52:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.61,0:52:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's like a physical, mental disease, it seems like it would be a lot less powerful than his state.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.41,0:52:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So how could that help drag him down?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.91,0:52:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it has to do with karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.11,0:52:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with maybe some entities that don't like anybody else getting up to 700.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.32,0:52:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But temporal lobe epilepsy is also often associated with religiosity and religious delusions, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.60,0:53:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, his experience is really different than anything I've had,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.29,0:53:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,because there's never been an other.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.96,0:53:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He felt he was getting dictation from an archangel.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.16,0:53:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never felt that any knowingness was coming from any other entity, you know, a guide or entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.17,0:53:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And at that point, he was calibrated well.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.17,0:53:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And three years later, he crashed down extremely low.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.97,0:53:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I clinically suspected that temporal lobe epilepsy had triggered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.52,0:53:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It created a vulnerability.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.12,0:53:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And in that vulnerability, he was taken over.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.12,0:53:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He was taken over by other entities.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.12,0:53:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The same thing happens with people that are in good condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.12,0:53:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In a state of intoxication, you're now vulnerable to lower astral possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.83,0:53:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people have become quite demonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.83,0:53:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And so what happened to him was a tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.98,0:53:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the cost to the world has been enormous,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.98,0:54:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,because in all those centuries since, it's been one continuous war.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.08,0:54:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And the number of people who have died as a result of that is in the hundreds of millions.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.11,0:54:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And the teachings that come out of Wahhabism calibrate at 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.17,0:54:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wahhab, calibrate him yourself, was at 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.49,0:54:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.49,0:54:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wahhab was 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.29,0:54:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So Wahhab, at 30, reinterpreted the teachings of Muhammad and came out with Wahhabism,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.29,0:54:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the backbone of Al-Qaeda and all the rest, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.29,0:54:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's one of the great tragedies of human evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.29,0:54:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.40,0:54:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle for dominion of this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.40,0:54:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a threat to that dominion, so they caught him where he was vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.80,0:54:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, I'd like to thank you for these tools, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.12,0:55:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's helped pull out some of those that I had in the closet, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.12,0:55:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and hone them and start using them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.12,0:55:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And I really appreciate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.12,0:55:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And I do have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.12,0:55:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,As the intellectual,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.12,0:55:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,does a person's...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.35,0:55:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,educational background limit you as far as what you can achieve in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.35,0:55:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,as far as...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.35,0:55:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In what words? Spiritual work?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.35,0:55:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In spiritual work, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.35,0:55:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.15,0:55:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.15,0:55:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.18,0:55:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, sometimes education gets in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.18,0:55:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To, you know, the teaching of Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.32,0:55:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the practice of the presence of God
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.72,0:55:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is just a little book.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.20,0:55:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The practice of the presence of God
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.20,0:55:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is just a little book.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.68,0:55:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Father what?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.68,0:55:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.87,0:55:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the practice of the presence of God
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.90,0:56:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,means that, you know, you could maybe finish third grade and still get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.90,0:56:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, the genuineness of his devotion and attention to it and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.03,0:56:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, it's very...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.06,0:56:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great classic.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.44,0:56:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you don't even have to go past third grade,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.44,0:56:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but you'd have to have somebody read it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.44,0:56:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.44,0:56:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.44,0:56:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.44,0:56:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.44,0:56:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.44,0:56:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The practice of the presence of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.44,0:56:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Brother Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.44,0:56:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It sits over the head of my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.44,0:56:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.96,0:56:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.96,0:56:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's simplicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.96,0:56:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Simplicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.96,0:56:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.96,0:56:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.30,0:56:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.30,0:56:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I appreciate your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.30,0:56:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.30,0:56:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You already signed my book.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.30,0:56:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you already signed my book.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.30,0:56:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.30,0:56:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you could give...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.30,0:56:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,raise the consciousness level of everyone here,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.30,0:56:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,just with a prayer, maybe,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.30,0:56:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,or just a little prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.30,0:56:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.30,0:56:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.30,0:56:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.30,0:56:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.30,0:56:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.30,0:56:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.30,0:56:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.30,0:56:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.30,0:56:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A little bit of the prayer, maybe,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.30,0:56:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,or a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.30,0:57:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And just let us have a little bit of what you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.52,0:57:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.16,0:57:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.16,0:57:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to share.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.25,0:57:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.25,0:57:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet we'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.02,0:57:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We do, every meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.02,0:57:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my high joy of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.95,0:57:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.95,0:57:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.95,0:57:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.57,0:57:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is on the origin of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.57,0:57:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,do they arise within the ultimate context, potentiality of God?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.84,0:57:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is God the creator of evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.89,0:57:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about different universes now.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.35,0:57:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There are different universes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.77,0:58:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In this universe, we talk about, during these lectures and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.09,0:58:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,it pertains to this universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.85,0:58:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It does not pertain to other dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.33,0:58:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The human assumes that his dimension
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.79,0:58:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and the God that goes with his dimension
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.49,0:58:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and the religion and all, it explains everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.13,0:58:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The universe has been going on forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.37,0:58:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's increasing at the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.80,0:58:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So this little putsy planet here is stuck in the middle of nowhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.88,0:58:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,like the outhouse of civilization here.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.30,0:58:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't include the explanation of all of creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.13,0:58:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wouldn't overburden religion or spirituality to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.42,0:58:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't expect it to be omniscient.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.96,0:58:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Omniscient.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.52,0:58:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a quality of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.92,0:58:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.87,0:58:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need omniscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.99,0:58:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason, I guess, the reason I ask the question is that
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.23,0:58:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,they're saying that all, like God, is the source of all creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.77,0:58:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.13,0:58:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then is God also the source of the possibility of evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.07,0:59:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.63,0:59:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Evil is a human term projected on that which denies the reality of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.43,0:59:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Not necessarily opposed, but denies it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.47,0:59:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't want to think in terms of opposites.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.84,0:59:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's light and then there's no light, and then we call it darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.16,0:59:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But darkness is not the enemy of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.30,0:59:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not a war between dark and light.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.20,0:59:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.54,0:59:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking, like, how inclusive is God?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.88,0:59:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it embrace all possibilities?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.50,0:59:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That which refuses or rejects the radiance of divinity posthumously finds a different realm in which to,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.72,0:59:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, evolve, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.20,0:59:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.90,0:59:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's beyond concern for spiritual students?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.73,0:59:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more an intellectual wonderment.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.27,0:59:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes when we ask the kinesiology, when we get off into wonderments like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.47,1:00:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,we often get a no.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.72,1:00:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And the reason is, what God's saying is you don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.06,1:00:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't distract yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.52,1:00:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a whole different dimension.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.00,1:00:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do that some other lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.88,1:00:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait until you're in some celestial realm,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.91,1:00:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and oh,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.43,1:00:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the guys up there do that, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.57,1:00:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But for you, in this lifetime, it's not necessary to know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.07,1:00:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So with humility, a lot of times we get a no, and I'm satisfied with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.19,1:00:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What God's saying is don't go there.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.51,1:00:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, leave it alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.97,1:00:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a whole thing in itself, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.33,1:00:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It could take a whole lifetime to resolve what you're asking here,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.49,1:00:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're going to open Pandora's box.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.27,1:00:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with it at this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.39,1:00:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.87,1:00:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know, and maybe you're not prepared for the answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.83,1:00:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So I always use kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.43,1:00:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we go there?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.43,1:00:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of times, it will get no.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.39,1:00:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go there now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.93,1:00:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.73,1:00:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't that you can't go there somewhere, or that it isn't legitimate,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.67,1:00:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but now is not the time or the place.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.59,1:00:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.11,1:00:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.91,1:00:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd also like to thank you very much because of all the benefits and teachings
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.71,1:01:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,people are exposed to.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.71,1:01:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll be going back to Hong Kong, where I'm originally from, next month.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.25,1:01:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.57,1:01:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd like to take this chance to thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.81,1:01:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.85,1:01:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to start our study group.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.42,1:01:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.70,1:01:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to start a study group in Hong Kong.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.64,1:01:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been to Hong Kong.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.26,1:01:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I was to Shanghai.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.50,1:01:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I never got to Hong Kong.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.42,1:01:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.53,1:01:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite a startling city when you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.73,1:01:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like New York City.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.89,1:01:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.93,1:01:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hong Kong.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.95,1:01:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.62,1:01:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.92,1:01:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.36,1:01:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.28,1:01:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from a study group here in Houston.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.88,1:01:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here in Houston.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.02,1:01:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.02,1:01:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wanted to thank you for showing me the path.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.84,1:01:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.34,1:01:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And for signing all of our papers.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.46,1:01:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being a part of a study group.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.32,1:01:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how AA started out, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.86,1:01:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first group.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.92,1:02:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And then they wrote down the 12 steps, the initial 12 traditions.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.56,1:02:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And other people just repeated them.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.34,1:02:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Little groups popped up here, hopped up there, popped up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.80,1:02:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And now they're by the millions, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.90,1:02:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just grassroots.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.16,1:02:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the group in Houston is definitely growing.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.12,1:02:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I love that.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.12,1:02:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.16,1:02:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.90,1:02:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We enjoyed it when you got to speak there at the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.17,1:02:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.85,1:02:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.25,1:02:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wonderful place.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.13,1:02:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.33,1:02:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.46,1:02:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.54,1:02:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.20,1:02:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a follow-up question to an earlier question.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.18,1:02:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.08,1:02:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's about once we understand about attachments
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.94,1:02:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and that we are addicted to attachments.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.66,1:02:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.06,1:02:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we understand that, how do we then do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.19,1:02:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They're difficult.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.86,1:02:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Difficult.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.58,1:02:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The attachment is difficult.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.00,1:03:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And it sometimes takes a lot of work to undo it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.92,1:03:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,An attachment.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.68,1:03:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that is appealing to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.94,1:03:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And is it the child, the adolescent, the adult?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.34,1:03:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it that it's appealing to, for one thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.10,1:03:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, I love kitties.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.38,1:03:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that appealing to?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.08,1:03:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My kid just loves kitties.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.80,1:03:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the kid in me, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.30,1:03:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So if a kitty gets run over, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.04,1:03:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the child in me is going to go into grief, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.51,1:03:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The adult in me says,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.21,1:03:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I need another cat like a colon head right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.03,1:03:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.59,1:03:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So you could look at, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.77,1:03:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,games people play, I think, was interesting
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.93,1:03:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the delineation of the child,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.55,1:03:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the adolescent, the adult, and ourselves, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.57,1:03:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and see which identification is it that's having the problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.51,1:03:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's helpful.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.53,1:03:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So all you can learn about it from various dimensions
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.99,1:03:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,tends to loosen it, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.30,1:03:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we then say, I surrender this to God?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.34,1:04:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it something we say, we think, we feel?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.00,1:04:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.41,1:04:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we actually surrender something?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.93,1:04:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.65,1:04:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.37,1:04:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So you pray for God to relieve you of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.17,1:04:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What you do is you substitute love for attachment.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.72,1:04:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can love everything without necessarily being attached.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.46,1:04:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Attached is wanting to control it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.09,1:04:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And love is letting it be free.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.69,1:04:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So the difference between attachment and love
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.91,1:04:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,is the willingness to control it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.60,1:04:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.86,1:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you love it, then nothing can...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.18,1:04:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't love it, then you have to give up the love.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.44,1:04:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Attachment is something different.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.44,1:04:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.88,1:04:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.88,1:04:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.20,1:04:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.20,1:04:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more to that question.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.20,1:04:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you're talking about a couple of years of therapy, really, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.84,1:04:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Attachment is really such a proclivity of the human mind
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.84,1:04:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that it takes a lot of work to not get attached to.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.08,1:04:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
