Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.12,1:12:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. After reading Power Versus Force, at least my impression was that the levels
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.20,1:12:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of teaching of Christianity dropped because of the debate that was going on, and they
