Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.10,1:13:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't take the Council of Nicaea apart.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.62,1:13:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I just said, what was the level of Christianity prior to and after to?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.96,1:14:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole, it's a whole study of religious history, to study all what went on around
