Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.18,1:17:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.18,1:17:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.18,1:17:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, here's the thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.18,1:17:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The principle that really hits home to me the most is the principle of positionalities
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.18,1:17:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and attachments, and those are the creation of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.18,1:17:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.18,1:17:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.18,1:17:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.18,1:17:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Projections.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.18,1:17:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.18,1:17:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.18,1:17:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, here's the thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.18,1:17:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, when he was asking about attachments before, I didn't have a chance to think about
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.18,1:17:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,it a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.18,1:17:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And after I thought about it a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.21,1:17:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But what you're attached to is the value that you have projected onto something.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.21,1:17:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, my answer now is complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.72,1:17:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you think you're attached to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.08,1:17:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.08,1:17:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the value you're attached to what you've projected onto it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.08,1:17:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You've glamorized it by the energy of like Alice Bailey says.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.08,1:17:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.08,1:17:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.08,1:17:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, here's my question.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.08,1:17:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You've enhanced its value by your own projection.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.08,1:17:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.08,1:17:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can live without another cat, see.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.08,1:17:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I go into depression, if something happens to one of these kittens, then that's
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.08,1:17:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,attachment, see.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.08,1:18:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm really trying to evolve spiritually, but I do know that for me personally, my big
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.08,1:18:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,stumbling block, my obstacle is the ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.08,1:18:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And the ego's got a huge amount of fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.08,1:18:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And the ego says, I will not let go.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.08,1:18:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I am in command.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.08,1:18:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you could please tell me what is a technique for me to let the ego relax and
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.08,1:18:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,let go of fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.08,1:18:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just let go of the ego as though it's a piece of paper.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.08,1:18:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a piece of ice, an ice cube or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.08,1:18:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's a complexity that's evolved since the beginning of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.56,1:18:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you how the ego began with the amoeba, the protozoa, the mouths up through
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.56,1:18:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,them.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.65,1:18:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's multiple identifications.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.65,1:18:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside of the human you, there's an animal you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.65,1:18:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.65,1:18:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.65,1:18:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Under appropriate conditions, you come out swinging, right?
