Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.65,1:18:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.65,1:18:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there's all kinds of aspects of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.65,1:18:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And it really takes really years of looking at yourself, introspection.
