Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.65,1:18:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.65,1:19:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, you know, surrendering what comes up, asking God to be your help, picking up
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.65,1:19:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritual energy of groups like this that give you the power to handle it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.65,1:19:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, you're doing the right thing by, first of all, bringing in as much information
