Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.68,1:19:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.68,1:19:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,See, that's why the spiritual teacher has to be somebody who has the power of having
