Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.16,1:19:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to kid you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.16,1:19:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It came up like terror of death.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.48,1:20:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The knowingness, there was just a knowingness there.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.48,1:20:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No voice, no other, no Archangel, you know, no Archangel Gabriel, nobody out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.48,1:20:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There was just the knowingness coming out of the vibrational energy of the aura.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.16,1:20:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All fear is illusion, surrender it no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.16,1:20:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I surrendered my life and the fear came up like terror.
