Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.38,1:21:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,To me creation is evolutionary.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.38,1:21:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, God's will is that this life form evolve, you see, this is the potentiality of evolution.
